examples.en: The cheese has a strong odor.
They recognized the odor at once.
A unique property of garlic is its strong odor.
This deodorant prevents bad odor from occurring.
The room had a suspect odor.
He whiffed a strong odor of perfume.
The odor spread throughout the room.
An unspeakable odor came sweeping into the room.
The kitchen had a yeasty odor.
An offensive odor was coming from the basement.
A wicked odor was coming from the closet.
